PN,41201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744483
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,FResident doctors across Northern
OL,6,FIreland are taking part in a 24-hour
OL,7,Fwalkout over pay.
OL,9,FThe strike started at 7am on Monday
OL,10,Fand will go on until 6.59am on Tuesday.
OL,12,FResident doctors in hospitals and GP
OL,13,Fsurgeries are staging the action amid
OL,14,Fa demand for full pay restoration.
OL,16,FIt follows strike action by
OL,17,Fconsultants and specialist doctors
OL,18,Flast week.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,FThe British Medical Association (BMA),
OL,6,Fa trade union and professional
OL,7,Forganisation which speaks for doctors,
OL,8,Fsaid that all doctors in Northern
OL,9,FIreland are in dispute with the
OL,10,FDepartment of Health.
OL,12,FThey said GPs are still in dispute
OL,13,Fwith the department over the
OL,14,Fimposition of the 2025/26 General
OL,15,FMedical Services (GMS) contract.
OL,17,FDr Steven Montgomery, chairman of
OL,18,FBMA's Northern Ireland resident
OL,19,Fdoctors committee (NIRDC), said they
OL,20,Ffeel they have been left with no
OL,21,Fchoice other than to strike.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"Pay erosion for resident doctors
OL,6,Fstill sits at up to 20% since 2008 and
OL,7,Fwe lag behind our colleagues in the
OL,8,Frest of the UK and in the south of
OL,9,FIreland on pay," he said.
OL,11,F"Add to that, growing patient numbers
OL,12,Fwithout the necessary number of
OL,13,Fdoctors needed to meet this demand and
OL,14,Fpressure, alongside younger doctors
OL,15,Flooking to leave the health service to
OL,16,Fwork elsewhere for better pay and
OL,17,Fworking conditions.
OL,19,F"It is unfortunately a perfect storm
OL,20,Ffor our health service."
OL,26,@mD@AOUqD@PO]sD@AOU{D@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,FHe added: "What does it say about our
OL,6,Fhealth service when all branches of
OL,7,Fpractice in medicine are in dispute
OL,8,Fwith the government?
OL,10,F"The health minister can bury his head
OL,11,Fin the sand about this problem all he
OL,12,Fwants but the numbers speak for
OL,13,Fthemselves: there are not enough
OL,14,Fdoctors to treat our growing, ageing
OL,15,Fpopulation as our waiting list crisis
OL,16,Fdemonstrates.
OL,26,@mD@KOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"We also know that over half of
OL,6,Fpenultimate and final year medical
OL,7,Fstudents studying in Northern Ireland
OL,8,Fare either planning to leave the
OL,9,Fcountry or are undecided once they
OL,10,Ffinish their foundation training, with
OL,11,Fpoor pay cited as the main reason.
OL,13,F"These medical students ` and us as
OL,14,Fresident doctors ` are the future
OL,15,Fconsultants, GPs and SAS (Specialty,
OL,16,FAssociate Specialist, and Specialist)
OL,17,Fdoctors that the Department of Health
OL,18,Fis dependent upon to meet growing
OL,19,Fpatient numbers and implement its
OL,20,Fplans for a neighbourhood model of
OL,21,Fcare."
OL,26,@mD@AOUuD@AOU}D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,FDr Montgomery has urged Health
OL,6,FMinister Mike Nesbitt to "engage in
OL,7,Fmeaningful negotiations towards pay
OL,8,Frestoration".
OL,10,F"It is unacceptable that doctors `
OL,11,Ffrontline health care staff ` have
OL,12,Fbeen once again forced into the
OL,13,Fposition of taking strike action to be
OL,14,Fheard, while government sits on its
OL,15,Fhands, counts on our goodwill and
OL,16,Fdelayed pay uplifts to keep the health
OL,17,Fservice going. This cannot continue,"
OL,18,Fhe said.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUpD@LO]rD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"We join our consultant and specialist
OL,6,Fdoctor colleagues in calling on
OL,7,Fgovernment to step in and resolve this
OL,8,Fdispute with a credible offer to avert
OL,9,Fstrike action and solve these disputes
OL,10,Fwithout delay."
OL,12,FIn response, Mr Nesbitt said he was
OL,13,F"disappointed" that the action had
OL,14,Fbeen taken.
OL,16,F"This follows a 24-hour period of
OL,17,Findustrial action by consultants and
OL,18,Fspecialist and associate specialist
OL,19,F(SAS) doctors Thursday into Friday
OL,20,Flast week," he said.
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@OO]uD@AOUuD@NO]xD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"It is important to stress that the
OL,6,Fvast majority of services across the
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care (HSC) system
OL,8,Fare proceeding as planned. All
OL,9,Fpatients with scheduled appointments
OL,10,Fon either day should attend as planned
OL,11,Funless they have been directly
OL,12,Fcontacted to advise their appointment
OL,13,Fhas been postponed. All trusts have
OL,14,Factivated their planning arrangements
OL,15,Fto ensure essential services are
OL,16,Fmaintained."
OL,26,@mD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,FMr Nesbitt said he remained committed
OL,6,Fto implementing the pay award as
OL,7,Frecommended by the independent
OL,8,FDoctors' and Dentists' Pay Review Body
OL,9,F(DDRB). But he said he was unable to
OL,10,Fdo so until Stormont ministers agreed
OL,11,Fa budget for the year.
OL,13,F"This action is being taken on the
OL,14,Fmandate of less than a quarter of the
OL,15,Fmedical workforce in Northern
OL,16,FIreland," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"Overall, only 24.8% of doctors
OL,6,Flocally have voted to take this
OL,7,Faction. I am very grateful to those
OL,8,Fwho recognise the impacts strike
OL,9,Faction will have on our population,
OL,10,Fand for their commitment to provide
OL,11,Fcontinuity of service.
OL,26,@mD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"The uplift recommended by the Review
OL,6,FBody for 26/27 is 3.5%, which is
OL,7,Fhigher than that for other healthcare
OL,8,Fprofessionals working in Health and
OL,9,FSocial Care (HSC). It comes on top of
OL,10,Fan average cumulative pay uplift over
OL,11,Fthe last three years of 30% for
OL,12,Fresident doctors, 25% for specialty,
OL,13,Fassociate specialist, and specialist
OL,14,Fdoctors (SAS doctors) and 24% for
OL,15,Fconsultants.
OL,26,@mD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"I recently met with the chairs of the
OL,6,Fthree relevant BMA committees and made
OL,7,Fclear my position. They made clear
OL,8,Fthat even the increase of 3.5% is
OL,9,Fnowhere near enough to satisfy their
OL,10,Fdemands. To go beyond the 3.5% as
OL,11,Frecommended by the independent pay
OL,12,Freview recommendation would have
OL,13,Fsignificant repercussions for nurses,
OL,14,Fteachers, police officers and indeed
OL,15,Fthe entire public sector workforce.
OL,16,FSo, calling on me to act fails to
OL,17,Frecognise this is an Executive
OL,18,Fdecision, a point I put to the BMA
OL,19,Frepresentatives.
OL,26,@mD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"I reiterate my commitment to ensuring
OL,6,FHSC colleagues receive their
OL,7,Frecommended 26/27 pay uplifts, despite
OL,8,Fthe unprecedented shortfall as
OL,9,Findicated in my draft budget. I value
OL,10,Fthe workforce above our buildings,
OL,11,Fbeds, equipment and medicines. But
OL,12,Fthere is simply no scope for pay
OL,13,Fawards beyond the recommendations of
OL,14,Fthe review bodies in 26/27.
OL,26,@mD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782744484
OL,3,CResident doctors strike over pay
OL,5,F"Finally, I want to pay a particular
OL,6,Ftribute to the many doctors, nurses,
OL,7,Fallied health professionals and
OL,8,Fexceptional support staff who will
OL,9,Fcontinue to deliver care and see
OL,10,Fpatients throughout the days of
OL,11,Fplanned industrial action."
OL,13,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,14,FITVX
OL,16,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,17,Fhere.
OL,26,@mD@AOUsD@[O]
